OL,3,CUK hotel chain bans aesthetic
OL,4,Ccompanies after woman has botched BBL
OL,6,FA major UK hotel chain has told ITV
OL,7,FNews that it has instructed all its
OL,8,Fvenues to not accept bookings from
OL,9,Fcosmetic companies after a woman
OL,10,Frequired hospital treatment following
OL,11,Fa botched procedure.
OL,13,FMalmaison, which describes itself as
OL,14,Foffering luxury boutique
OL,15,Faccommodation, has banned aesthetic
OL,16,Fcompanies from operating out of its
OL,17,Fvenues after an invasive procedure was
OL,18,Fcarried out on its premises.
