OL,6,FThe hotel chain informed ITV News:
OL,7,F"Invasive medical procedures are not
OL,8,Fallowed on our premises. All hotels in
OL,9,Four UK estate have been instructed to
OL,10,Fnot accept any bookings from such
OL,11,Fcompanies and reminded to thoroughly
OL,12,Fvet all enquiries that are cosmetic or
OL,13,Fmedical in nature."
OL,15,FIn February, a woman attended an
OL,16,Fappointment at the Newcastle Malmaison
OL,17,Fand had a non-surgical or filler
OL,18,FBrazilian Butt Lift (BBL).
