OL,3,CUK hotel chain bans aesthetic
OL,4,Ccompanies after woman has botched BBL
OL,6,FThe procedure involves hundreds of
OL,7,Fmillilitres of cosmetic fluid - known
OL,8,Fas filler - being injected into the
OL,9,Fbuttocks to achieve a larger bum.
OL,11,FBut, as ITV News has reported, the
OL,12,Fhigh-risk treatment has left dozens of
OL,13,Fwomen contracting serious infections
OL,14,Fand, in some cases, requiring
OL,15,Femergency surgery.
OL,17,FITV News understands that the client
OL,18,Fwho had the BBL in the Newcastle hotel
OL,19,Fbranch has been treated in hospital.
