OL,3,CUK hotel chain bans aesthetic
OL,4,Ccompanies after woman has botched BBL
OL,6,FSpeaking anonymously to ITV News, the
OL,7,Fwoman said: "The pain I went through
OL,8,Ffor 10 weeks was indescribable - on
OL,9,Ftop of the trauma of not being able to
OL,10,Fsee my children when in hospital.
OL,12,F"I've been left scarred physically and
OL,13,Fmentally and would tell anyone
OL,14,Fthinking of having this procedure to
OL,15,Favoid it."
OL,17,FMalmaison said in a statement: "We
OL,18,Ftake the health, safety and wellbeing
OL,19,Fof all our guests and visitors
OL,20,Fextremely seriously and were very
OL,21,Fconcerned to hear about this case."
