OL,6,FThis incident comes as Glasgow City
OL,7,FCouncil announced that it has from
OL,8,Fcarrying out BBLs in the city's
OL,9,Fgrounds.
OL,11,FIt follows another woman experiencing
OL,12,Facute pain and a serious infection.
OL,13,FShe had a liquid BBL in a conference
OL,14,Froom in the Glasgow Holiday Inn City
OL,15,FCentre Theatreland.
OL,17,FShe wanted to remain anonymous, but
OL,18,Ftold ITV News that she was admitted to
OL,19,Fhospital in significant pain and
OL,20,Freceived antibiotics.
